Just because new version of caffeine (https://launchpad.net/caffeine) don't work for me.
Icons from caffeine is used.
To install:

$ sudo cp caffeine-cup-full.svg /usr/share/icons/hicolor/scalable/status/caffeine-cup-full.svg
$ sudo cp caffeine-cup-empty.svg /usr/share/icons/hicolor/scalable/status/caffeine-cup-empty.svg
$ sudo cp mcaffeine.py /usr/bin/mcaffeine
$ chmod +x /usr/bin/mcaffeine

script just run 
	xset dpms 0 0 0
or
	xset dmps 0 0 200
when user click icon in system tray.
but you can add your own commands.
